cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Voctomix 2.0 — Full-HD software live video mixer for reproducible remote production"
abstract: >-
  An evolution of the C3VOC voctomix live video mixer (voctocore + voctogui),
  extended with a three-state stream blanker, dynamic on-air titling, audio-follows-video,
  a telemetry service over HTTP and RabbitMQ, and a containerized deployment stack
  validated across single-PC, two-PC, Docker Compose and Kubernetes scenarios.
type: software
authors:
